1. Must be either a paralegal, JD, or licensed attorney
2. Must hold a CJIS (Criminal Justice Information Systems) certification
3. Must be available minimum of 40 hours per week for the duration of the review during standard business hours; No concurrent document review or other legal employment permitted while working with HaystackID unless cleared with us.
4. Clear criminal background check
5. Registered on https://reviewright.haystackid.com and completed the assessment.
